e, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143724, "create_time": 1653392938, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 导师怎么样，给指导吗", "timestamp": 1653392938}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143728, "create_time": 1653392985, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 老板们现在都觉得五年毕业是提前毕业了，老板们之间也内卷", "timestamp": 1653392985}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143740, "create_time": 1653393143, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 导师人挺好的，只是给的职业建议不太靠谱，这方面有点私心，也是给我带来困惑的点。因为我没有一开始打算走学术，后来想走学术是想一边学术一遍搞自己的副业，后来意识到学界现在异常卷，这种想法不靠谱之后，实际上跟老师利益相合点不多了，因为学界给的实在太少了。家里穷没办法", "timestamp": 1653393143}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143742, "create_time": 1653393164, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 导师学术上还是很勤奋，很靠谱的", "timestamp": 1653393164}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143744, "create_time": 1653393174, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re 洞主: 读博期间生活如何啊，压力大吗", "timestamp": 1653393174}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143745, "create_time": 1653393213, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 从我读博以来，我导师没给我一点指导，唉", "timestamp": 1653393213}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143746, "create_time": 1653393227, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 出去交流了，含金量增加有限，门槛低的东西也不太值钱其实。。。加上交流遇见疫情，效果也有限", "timestamp": 1653393227}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143750, "create_time": 1653393284, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Grace: 生活还好，压力比较大，两鬓斑白了。。", "timestamp": 1653393284}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143759, "create_time": 1653393351, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 其实也是好事，有空摸鱼去实习，我们就不太有条件了", "timestamp": 1653393351}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143760, "create_time": 1653393358, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 整个博士生涯有规划嘛？非工科博0想要参考", "timestamp": 1653393358}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143765, "create_time": 1653393373, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re 洞主: patpat，压力来源是什么啊，会影响睡眠吗（之前听说有些博士生读着慢慢失眠了，有点害怕）", "timestamp": 1653393373}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143768, "create_time": 1653393506, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 借助清华的平台，早点找大佬带发顶刊，早期可以找一些年轻的rising star合作一下，他们还是很愿意和低年级的博士合作的，可以帮着带入行。这是学术路线的", "timestamp": 1653393506}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143774, "create_time": 1653393596, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 去业界的话，早点找到靠谱课题，早点实习，近年找工作博士也不通杀了，也卷的很，早做打算", "timestamp": 1653393596}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143779, "create_time": 1653393637, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Grace: 论文结果的不确定性，毕业时间的不确定性，机会成本越积累越大的无力感", "timestamp": 1653393637}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143782, "create_time": 1653393661, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 谢谢dz!", "timestamp": 1653393661}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 143785, "create_time": 1653393695, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "世另我", "timesta